Post-Doctoral Fellow, <a href="https://www.gcr21.org">Käte Hamburger Kolleg / Centre for Global Cooperation Research</a>, Universität Duisburg–Essen. Projekt: Culture as Resource and Diplomacy: Between Geopolitics and Issues-Based Policy.</li>
